00:03:15.890 --> 00:03:17.910
And then you get that same value.

00:03:17.910 --> 00:03:20.313
You still get to zero.

00:03:20.313 --> 00:03:22.205
So that's, I know if that helps or hurts

00:03:22.205 --> 00:03:24.225
